    "description": "Fear the Phantom is a CO-OP paranormal investigation game. Play alone, or with up to 3 other players. When playing with others, you can even play as the ghost.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262550/extras/e3bd89e062c2d4c6426158ef0e3aa7f1.webp?t=1754500234\" width=600 height=60 /></span><br><strong>This game is not for the faint hearted. With evil beings lurking around every corner, you are never safe.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262550/extras/13aa63138a82ceaa63f199650c8b1265.poster.avif?t=1754500234\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262550/extras/13aa63138a82ceaa63f199650c8b1265.webm?t=1754500234\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262550/extras/13aa63138a82ceaa63f199650c8b1265.mp4?t=1754500234\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262550/extras/2837b825041bbe0ec6ab07f465b3ec64.webp?t=1754500234\" width=600 height=60 /></span><br><strong>You are not completely helpless. You have equipment that helps you identify the type of spirit you're dealing with, which you then have to exorcise accordingly.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262550/extras/2f439e6ce59241251bee7541b2867e7a.poster.avif?t=1754500234\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262550/extras/2f439e6ce59241251bee7541b2867e7a.webm?t=1754500234\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262550/extras/2f439e6ce59241251bee7541b2867e7a.mp4?t=1754500234\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>CO-OP cloud based multiplayer.</li><li>Intense PvP with a learning curve.</li><li>Singleplayer mode.</li><li>A lot of various equipment with different uses.</li><li>Dark atmosphere with immersive ambiance.</li><li>Proximity chat. The players can communicate when close to each other. The ghost can eavesdrop, but the players cannot hear the ghost talking.</li></ul>",
